  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
      <div rend="parallel">
        <p xml:id="NA69-kiḷavi">itu viṉaivayiṟ pirita lāṟṟāḷāya talaivi colliyatu.</p>
        <p xml:lang="en">This is what SHE said who was unable to bear [HIS] separating for the sake of wealth.</p>
      </div>
      <div rend="parallel">
        <lg xml:id="NA69">
<l>            palkatir maṇṭilam pakalcey tāṟṟic</l>
<l>            cēyuyar peruvaraic ceṉṟavaṇ maṟaiyap</l>
<l>            paṟavai pārppuvayiṉ aṭaiyap puṟaviṉ</l>
<l>            māyerut tiralai maṭappiṇai taḻuva</l>
<l>            mullai mukaivāy tiṟappap palvayiṟ </l>
<l>            ṟōṉṟi tōṉṟupu putalviḷak kuṟāa</l>
<l>            matarvai nallāṉ māci ṟeṇmaṇi</l>
<l>            koṭuṅkōṟ kōvalar kuḻalō ṭoṉṟi</l>
<l>            yaituvan ticaikku maruḷiṉ mālai</l>
<l>            yāḷviṉaik kakaṉṟōr ceṉṟa nāṭṭu </l>
<l>            miṉaiya vākit tōṉṟiṉ</l>
<l>            viṉaivalit tamaita lāṟṟalar maṉṉē.</l>
            </lg>
       <lg xml:lang="en">
<l rend="indent">When the many-beamed disk, having ably made the day,</l>
<l rend="indent">goes to the great mountains in distant height [and] hides there,</l>
<l rend="indent">when the birds settle with [their] young ones, in the woodland,</l>
<l rend="indent">when the black-necked Iralai embraces [his] youthful doe,</l>
<l rend="indent">when the jasmine buds open [their] mouths, on many sides,</l>
<l rend="indent">when the shrubs are made to have lamps, since the Malabar lilies</l>
<l rend="indent4">appeared,</l>
<l rend="indent">when the flawless clear bell of the exhilarated good cows</l>
<l rend="indent">becomes one with the flute of the cowherds with bent sticks,</l>
<l rend="indent">comes over beautifully [and] sounds</l>
<l rend="indent3">– evenings without consideration,</l>
<l rend="indent2">if they appear to be like that also in the land</l>
<l rend="indent2">where he has gone who has departed for manly work,</l>
<l>he really cannot be content, compelled by work.<note place="foot">The second possibility is here to take <term xml:lang="ta">amai</term> as an auxiliary: "he really cannot be permanently be kept back by work."</note></l>
        </lg>
         </div>
